        </div>
          </div>
        <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
          <img class="card-img-top" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2204196/pexels-photo-2204196.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=750&w=1260" alt="Man Spotting Another Man Lifting">
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="home-card-text">Select your activity, time, location and begin chatting with likeminded people.</p>
        </div>
          </div>
      </div>
